<h2 id=3D"1">Dune 3.23.0</h2>
<div class=3D"outline-text-2" id=3D"text-1">
<p>
Archive: <a href=3D"https://discuss.ocaml.org/t/ann-dune-3-23-0/18055/1">ht=
tps://discuss.ocaml.org/t/ann-dune-3-23-0/18055/1</a>
</p>
